    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Can somebody help me?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’m hurting! I’m dying! Does anyone care?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I have an urgent need!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But sadly it seems that no one is aware."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Wait, a priest I see!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Descending like me. My case he’ll claim!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He passes by me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then comes a Levite and does the same."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I thought they would help me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They seemed to serve God and to honor His name."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Religion is empty!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It cannot heal me. All my wounds still remain."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A Samaritan"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Comes upon me and observes my plight."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Moved with compassion"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He treats my wounds, binding them just right."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus You found me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You poured oil and wine on my wounds, them to heal!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You put me on Your beast!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "At last! Here is kindness and tenderness real."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now I’m in the inn,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church, with all those under Your care."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And now I begin"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To find some others still in despair."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, bring in more wounded!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Those without the Spirit and the life divine."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That they could be added,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And at Your return, the same care You would find."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
